{"arkId":"cl010359754","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010359754","modified ":"2026-01-17","title":"vase","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"vase"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Vases de formes diverses"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Chypriote r\u00e9cent (-1600 - -1050)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-1600,"endYear":-1050,"imprecision":"","text":"Chypriote r\u00e9cent","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"1652","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"1652","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"flacon\r\n\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Flacon, dit \u0022bilbil\u0022, \u00e0 l\u00e8vre \u00e9vas\u00e9e, embouchure \u00e9troite et anse plate. Le col haut et cylindrique est soulign\u00e9 au niveau de l\u0027attache sup\u00e9rieure de l\u0027anse par deux anneaux plastiques. La panse ovo\u00efde repose sur un pied conique creux. \r\nCet objet appartient \u00e0 la cat\u00e9gorie \u0022Base-Ring Ware\u0022 (dont le nom renvoie \u00e0 la base annulaire des vases de ce type) qui d\u00e9signe une c\u00e9ramique model\u00e9e dont les parois dures et minces produisent un son m\u00e9tallique. Cette vaisselle brune est caract\u00e9ristique du Bronze r\u00e9cent I et II de Chypre. On en trouve \u00e9galement en Syrie, en Palestine et en Egypte. Ces flacons devaient contenir des mati\u00e8res pr\u00e9cieuses, tels des parfums ou encore de l\u0027opium, comme cela a \u00e9t\u00e9 avanc\u00e9 en raison de la forme du vase, que l\u0027on a compar\u00e9e \u00e0 une capsule de pavot.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"13,5","displayDimension":"13,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"7","displayDimension":"7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : terre cuite (brun orang\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : engobe (brun)","placeOfCreation":"Chypre","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"Chypre","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"mode d\u0027acquisition inconnu","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e Joseph D\u00e9chelette, Roanne","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"mode d\u0027acquisition inconnu"}],"denomination":[{"value":"vase"}],"material":[{"value":"terre cuite"}],"technic":[{"value":"engobe"}],"description":[{"value":"flacon"}],"place":[{"value":"Chypre"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000359754\/0000510759_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000359754\/0000510759_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2009 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Daniel Leb\u00e9e\/Carine Deambrosis","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000359754\/0001321913_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000359754\/0001321913_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2025 Mus\u00e9e du Louvre \/ D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","type":"vue d\u0027ensemble","position":1},{"